      <description>&lt;main class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"&gt; &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"&gt;&lt;h1 class="wp-block-post-title"&gt;Arc 10 password&amp;nbsp;locked&lt;/h1&gt;  &lt;div style="font-style:italic;font-weight:400;" class="wp-block-post-date has-small-font-size"&gt;&lt;time datetime="2024-10-15T21:00:37+11:00"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/2024/10/15/arc-10-password-locked/"&gt;October 15th, 2024&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained"&gt; &lt;p&gt;LN12 is out in English, so I did my thing.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;What&amp;#8217;s the password? Find it in the discord server.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;As is tradition when I take down chapters, the locked chapters have undergone a minor edit, polish, or rewrite depending on how much the original version bothered me. Chapters with major changes have an edited date on the top of the page. (I haven&amp;#8217;t gone through all the chapters yet.)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/2024/10/15/arc-10-password-locked/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-130534757-4919-671ac6954d595' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/index.html?ver=20241024#blog_id=130534757&amp;amp;post